      "note": "Form-ColorPicker — lazy-load on first popover:open per ADR-0025 (9e cascade after ADR-0011/0012/0013/0018/0020/0022/0023/0024). @melloware/coloris ^0.x — theme-aware via CSS vars, HSV/HSL/RGB/HEX modes, alpha opt-in, preset palette."
